      <title>乌克兰战争结束后俄罗斯将蓄势待发</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-22/why-russia-is-facing-a-crime-wave-when-war-on-ukraine-ends</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯派出大量士兵参加乌克兰战争，导致乌克兰犯罪率在入侵开始后不久就下降。如今，他们的归来又引发了一波犯罪浪潮。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-22/why-russia-is-facing-a-crime-wave-when-war-on-ukraine-ends</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 22 Jun 2024 06:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
