    <item>
      <title>里希·苏纳克 (Rishi Sunak) 7 月大选赌注似乎要失败的一周</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-22/the-week-that-rishi-sunak-s-july-election-bet-seemed-to-go-bust</link>
      <description><![CDATA[里希·苏纳克的顾问们早就知道，他不太可能赢得英国大选。本周，当他们收到内部民意调查结果，证实首相将面临最糟糕的情况时，他们私下接受了失败，并将注意力转移到确保保守党的生存上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-22/the-week-that-rishi-sunak-s-july-election-bet-seemed-to-go-bust</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 22 Jun 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
