      <title>泰国总理首次电视谈话中宣传赌场、核电计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-22/thai-pm-touts-plans-for-casinos-nuclear-power-in-first-tv-talk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国总理斯雷塔·塔维辛利用他作为国家领导人的首次月度电视讲话，推动赌场合法化计划，以遏制非法赌博，并建设核电站，以降低电力成本。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-22/thai-pm-touts-plans-for-casinos-nuclear-power-in-first-tv-talk</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 22 Jun 2024 03:05:16 GMT</pubDate>
