      <title>保罗·佩洛西的袭击者也被州法院判处绑架罪</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-06-21/urgent-attacker-of-nancy-pelosi-s-husband-also-found-guilty-of-kidnapping-and-could-face-more-prison-time</link>
      <description><![CDATA[旧金山（美联社）——一名男子因袭击前众议院议长南希·佩洛西的丈夫而被判处 30 年联邦监禁，周五他被判定犯有加重绑架罪，该罪名将被判处终身监禁，不得假释。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-06-21/urgent-attacker-of-nancy-pelosi-s-husband-also-found-guilty-of-kidnapping-and-could-face-more-prison-time</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 23:19:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>更多亚洲领导人希望加入金砖国家，习近平和普京获胜</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/more-asian-nations-want-to-join-putin-and-xi-in-expanded-brics</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本周，俄罗斯总统普京和中国国务院总理李强分别在东南亚结束会晤之际，金砖国家经济集团的这两个合作伙伴遇到了一个渴望加入该组织的地区，该组织被视为对冲西方主导的机构。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/more-asian-nations-want-to-join-putin-and-xi-in-expanded-brics</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 01:00:30 GMT</pubDate>
